{"tid":545842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院今起加強保安措施 所有人乖乖排隊","createTime":"2018-01-31T02:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T02:38:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6f436a0fa8a14a29c9c3efee6e233b76855380","tid":545842,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180131/large/1517364763_a353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F1517364763_a353.jpg&h=446c5fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司法機構於今天起加強高等法院大樓的保安措施，所有進入法院低層四樓法庭，以及一至十四樓任何樓層的人士，均需先於高院大堂接受保安檢查、通過金屬探測門或接受手提式金屬探測器監測，隨身物品亦需受到檢查。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構會將按使用者的身份分流，如公眾人士（包括上庭的被告和旁聽人士）、大律師和律師及傳媒，而法官、法庭職員和有需要進入法庭的執法部門人士，則可經特別通道毋須接受安檢。至於低層四樓的法庭，亦會安排保安人員以手提式探測器進行安檢程序。<br />\n<br />\n基於保安考慮，法庭使用者不准帶備液體進入管制區區域，法庭會放置水桶讓公眾將液體倒掉始可進入法庭，各樓層均設有飲水機和飲品自動販賣機。另外所有可作武器的如刀、鉸剪、鎅刀、鏍絲批等物品均一律不准帶入法庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180131/57774838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57774838&d=8Bx7RVfFyB9QLKvfWl4srI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=14c2dc60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57774838&h=ce8de6d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180131/57774838</a>"},{"pid":"c7e8081864c09468e9e67e205a8ad619a1283242","tid":545842,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}